- Initial value: 13000000.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
- End value: 13000000.00 (as of 2024-01-29)

This line item represents the total amount of capital that shareholders have invested in the company in exchange for shares. Since the values are the same at both dates, it suggests that no additional capital was contributed or withdrawn during this period.
